# Keep the build context small and never copy local-only / sensitive files into
# the image. Dependencies are installed fresh via `npm ci`; data/ and secrets
# come from the mounted volume and host .env at runtime.

# Dependencies & build output (reinstalled / rebuilt in the image)
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
*.tsbuildinfo

# Local data & secrets (mounted volume + env_file provide these at runtime)
data
.env
.env.*

# VCS / tooling / editor noise
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
.claude
.dmux
coverage
*.lcov

# Docs and local artifacts not needed to run the app
*.md
Codebase review request.zip
design_handoff_responsive_rail
nightly
docs

# OS cruft
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
